Manual therapy, exercise therapy, or both, in addition to usual care, for 
osteoarthritis of the hip or knee. 2: economic evaluation alongside a randomized 
controlled trial.

Pinto D(1), Robertson MC, Abbott JH, Hansen P, Campbell AJ; MOA Trial Team.

Collaborators: Abbott JH, Baxter GD, Campbell A, Robertson MC, Theis JC, 
Herbison P, de la Barra SL, McKenzie J, Basford J, Fitzgerald GK, Flynn T, Fritz 
J, Hansen P, Hurley-Osing D, Whitman J, McNamara D, Chapple C, Pinto D, Wright 
A, Kidd M, Higgs C, Smith J, Tumilty S, Kennedy E, Braund R, Cleland J, Cook C, 
Dockerty J, Nicholson H.

Author information:
(1)Department of Physical Therapy and Human Movement Sciences, Institute for 
