Basu S(1)(2)(3)(4), Seligman H(5), Bhattacharya J(2)(6).

Author information:
(1)Prevention Research Center, Department of Medicine, Stanford University, 
Stanford, CA, USA (SB).
(2)Centers for Health Policy, Primary Care and Outcomes Research, Stanford 
